Name:           perl-Unicode-EastAsianWidth
Version:        12.0
Release:        4%{?dist}
License:        CC0
Vendor:         Microsoft Corporation
Distribution:   Azure Linux
URL:            https://metacpan.org/release/Unicode-EastAsianWidth
